title: 13 Piece Brush Set With Case
description: This brush set comes with 12 brushes in a leatherine case. All brushes have long wooden handles and are a blend of sable and goat hair. The only synthetic brushes are the oval taklon concealer and the angle taklon liner brush.

title: Scunci No Damage Ponytail Holders, 30 ea
description: Scunci effortless beauty no-damage black elastics are your secret to effortless all-day hold. slide into any situation without worrying about hair slippage. large soft metal-free elastic bands keep ponytails tight while working out or for casual style and won't damage hair. 30 pack ensures that no matter where you put one down you'll always be able to pick one up. basic black color - as essential as the little black dress.

title: 10 Pairs of Reusable Thick False Eyelashes
description: Experience this thick and voluminous false eyelashes for your evening date, party, or prom! Make your eyes look bright and attractive! The eyelashes are long enough, which allows them to be cut and shaped to fit the contour for you eyes. The 100% hand made product is reusable when you remove it properly.

title: Scunci Effortless Beauty Thick Hair Mini Jaw Clips, 1 cm, 18-Count
description: With scunci effortless beauty hair accessories a woman should never have a bad hair day. scunci mini jaw clips can be used in a variety of ways. mini jaw clips create sectioned styles and conveniently hold small sections of hair for cutting, curling or drying. interlocking jaws hold even thick hair in place. small size makes them deal for children. basic black, clear for unobtrusive hold and tortoise brown for neutral hold.
